high_descs: Take the potato in the counter top
The potato moves towards the fridge
Open the fridge put it to the potato and take it again
Place the potato on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Take the potato in the counter top Place the potato on the counter top

high_descs: Turn around, go towards the wall, when you reach the wall, turn right to the countertop.
Turn around, go forward, turn left. Reach the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the potato on the left on the second level, close the fridge for thirteen seconds. Take the potato, close the fridge.
Turn around, go forward, turn right to face the countertop.
Place the potato on the countertop on the left.
anns.task_desc: Find a potato, cool it in the fridge, place it on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the counter top.
Take the potato from the counter top.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the potato into the fridge.
Then take it out and go near the counter top.
Put the potato on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put the potato on the counter top.
